asset_description: How goes it! I'm Garfunkel Flabtooth. I'm pretty sure I'm part octopus, I hope that doesn't bother you. You should know that I'm obsessed with catching the world's first faun, and I won't rest until I do. Pffft, whatever.

*Wink* I'm Young Fancynoice. I'm really trying to become a master Professional Mourner. Spending my nights staying woke probably isn't helping, though. I once tried to stalk Michael Cera. It did not end well for me.

Hello. My name is Kitty #763022. I have no idea how I got here, but I know it involves maxi dresses and a dragon. I can sing every Crazytown song by heart. I'm actually thinking of starting a cover album. Was your dad a boxer? Because damn, you’re a knockout!

G'day! I'm 💙 Lapis 💙 Garnet. What's your favourite hobby? Mine is talking about how much I lift. I can't get enough of it. I have made a mixtape for a duet with Janis Joplin, but I'm having a hard time tracking them down. You can help, right? Good talk, catch ya later!

Dia dhuit, I'm Clover! Oof, I rode in here on a rainbow and those things aren't as soft as they look. Have you seen my pot o' gold? I swear I left it right here... Oh well, I don't need piles o' shinies to know I'm the luckiest cat in the KittyVerse––I get to hang out with you!

Hi-ya! I'm Kitty #223213. I'm a Train Conductor by day, and I like riverdancing by night. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their snap-backs and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. I hope we can be pawmates.
Hi! Tweety Kat #2 S1 here. I'm here to enjoy chasing string and watching game shows. It wasn't heavily publicized, but I once had a brief relationship with Bagheera. I hope we can be friends.

*hissing noises*! I'm Aliena ///. I want to live in a world where people believe that one day cats will rule this planet. In my free time, I can usually be found voluptuous or sleeping in fresh laundry. Will you be the maple syrup to my garlic butter?

Hi-ya! I'm Ragdoll Spock Dali. All you need to know about me is I hate ice cream with a passion. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their snap-backs and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. Purrhaps this is the beginning of a beautiful relationship.

Good day. I'm Yoyo Pingnana, and I will do almost anything for a pair of Yeezys. Did you know sometimes when we touch, the honesty's too much? I know, crazy right? I've been mistaken for Oliver because I'm so good at vomiting on the carpet. I'm going to show you the time of your life.

Hi-ya. My name is parent dracula. I make a mean garlic casserole. If you want to join me and my clique, you should know that on Wednesdays we wear pink. Are you a parking ticket? ‘Cause you’ve got fine written all over you.

Yikes! You scared me. My parents named me Lavender & Dune Combo. just to distract myself from the staggering indifference of the universe. My best feature? My cankle, obviously. I can't imagine being with any other breeder now that I've met you!
Oy. You may call me 1670259. If I could be anybody in the world, it would be Pauly D. Leave me.
Hi, I'm 1697484. And you are? My best dress-up costume ever was when I impersonated Sandy Cheeks. Someday, all of this will be yours.

Greetings, kind purr! My name's 2Wt Page#4806 G9 and I'm a very good and clever kitten with a lot to offer the world! I have squired with the greatest of knights: there was Sir Face (they were a bit shallow), Sir Port (a very kind cat), and of course, Sir Prise (she was amazing). And now I have you! Gosh! I must be the luckiest kitten in the world!

"Why so serious?" I'm often asked. I guess they're not used to staring at the eyes of cosmic wrath itself. I am Virgin: Mars. Fancy., the god of war, anger, and destruction... Wait, I think Phobos wants to play. Come here, my Itty Bitty moon.

Good day! I'm Pure Spock. My cousin twice removed is John F. Kennedy Jr. I'm convinced that dogs are robot aliens who plan to take over Earth. One day I'll prove it. Honey, you wouldn't wanna see these claws come out.

Hi-ya! My name's Founder Cat #44. I once peed on Mother Theresa's cat. They had it coming. In my free time, I can usually be found voluptuous or siring for status. This will be an amewsing friendship.
Yo! I'm Kitty #52240. I've never told anyone this, but I once snuggled a dog. My secret indulgence is cereal. Purrhaps this is the beginning of a beautiful relationship.
Jambo! I'm Tora Hyperkins. Pleased to meet you. If I could be anybody in the world, it would be Spongebob. Alright, alright, alright.

Dia dhuit, I'm Purebred: Clover. 3x Doubles.! Oof, I rode in here on a rainbow and those things aren't as soft as they look. Have you seen my pot o' gold? I swear I left it right here... Oh well, I don't need piles o' shinies to know I'm the luckiest cat in the KittyVerse––I get to hang out with you!
Hey, what's up, hello. I'm liger shale. The "h" is silent. My new life goal is to catch a demigod and make it share its powers with me. Until our next encounter...

Yo! I'm rare gold ragdoll. In high school, I was voted school jock. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their snap-backs and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. In time you'll learn how purrfect I am.

Hi-ya! I'm 親ヤドギリ. All you need to know about me is I hate salad with a passion. I once dreamed of being a Dispensary Clerk. Now I can be found sleeping in fresh laundry all day. I hope we can be pawmates.

Aloha! Kitty #364072 here. I'm here to enjoy licking doorknobs and picking flowers. I once dreamed of being a Train Conductor. Now I can be found braiding people's hair all day. In time you'll learn how purrfect I am.
Shalom! I'm Kitty #132347. I'm a professional Mad Scientist and I love cereal. I'm convinced that that one day cats will rule this planet. One day I'll prove it. Can't wait to eat apple pie with you!

Hey cutie. I'm Big Fluffybaloo. Do you want to watch me fad dieting? I sure hope so. Ever think it's weird that you never see King Henry VIII and Sandra Bullock in the same place at the same time? Come, I'll show you my collection of peanut butter.

Well look who it is. I'm Purrbados: 4/4: Salt01, student of Balthazaar of the Unknown Lands. My college voted me "class clown", but I was always more interested in trying to swallow ribbons. Can you explain where babies come from? Asking for a friend...
Noice! I'm Wrecked 35. 4x Double Traits., get it right. I'm well-educated, don't worry. Can you help me get past the part in Pokémon Red that I can't beat?
*winces*, my name is Noodles Awesomesmoosh, but I'll also respond to Justice. Ever think it's weird that you never see Cleopatra and Michael Cera in the same place at the same time? Don't @ me.

*waves*! I'm Kitska Zappytime. I enjoy reciting poetry, breakdancing, and spinning sick beats. In my free time, I can usually be found fabulous or practicing witchcraft. We're so fur-tunate to have found each other!

I might appear to be a simple talisman, but if you take me into the realm of the Citadel you can reveal my true power: they call me VIRGIN. Purebred: Sully. Tally! No god can control me, but all will try. And if they succeed in collecting every talisman, who knows what power they could wield?

Sup playa! My name is Final Frontier & Daemonwings.. Let's get to know each other better. I heard a rumour Kristen Wiig was running for president. They'd have my vote. Don't pull my tail. Unless I ask.

Who goes there. My name is Reindeer #356. As a young kitten, I was always photography, but I think I've grown out of that. Sometimes, when I'm winning hearts and minds, I can't help but think about the superficial oracle. What do you say you and me get outta here?

Prrawr! I'm Draco Junior. 5 Multi Traits., and someday they will sing the tale of my great and terrible fire! Right meow, though, I'm mostly sticking to marshmallows... but they get totally toasty! If you don't want to get toasted to a purrfect golden brown, you'd better leave my cave now!
Who dares enter Catnap Hollow!? Oh, it's you. I'm Jack. Apologies for losing my head back there. Can you blame me? I've got this fiery pain in my neck, and my noggin is killing me.
What gives! The name's Peppermint Martian Dragon.. Whenever I eat cantaloupe my pee turns ochre. Is that normal? Let's go composing poems together!

Good day. I'm Landlubber & Roadtogold. RARE.. I'm magnificent and childish, and sometimes even suggestive. I ate pizza with salsa on it and now my tummy hurts. I can't believe you'd show your face around here.
Heyo! I'm Kitty #91819. I believe the world is flat. In my free time, I can usually be found seductive or volunteering at the local kitten rescue shelter. In time you'll learn how purrfect I am.
Good day! I'm Rondo. I believe the world is flat. My secret indulgence is chocolate. We can be friends, but keep the ultra purrsonal stuff to yourself, please.

I'm Pizzazz: Spangled X3. FANCY., and I'm as hot as melting cheese, as spicy as Italian sausage, and as well-loved as anchovies. (...In Metropurrlis they're the most popular topping.) Don't you dare bring up pineapple, it doesn't belong on pizza. Not to be extra cheesy, but I'll give you a pizza my heart.
*waves*! I'm VIRGIN G4 cymric. My friends describe me as fabulous and voluptuous. I once made a dog kiss. Our friendship will be fabulous, voluptuous, and full of chocolate.

Aloha! I'm Kitty #457374. My friends describe me as prickly and ridiculous. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their oversized sweaters and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. I like your face.

Sup playa! I'm Dual Jewel Gerbil Cottoncandy. My friends describe me as brilliant and gorgeous. I am 12% hobbit, 48% Dogwalker, and otherwise bad at math. I can't wait to wake you up at 4am for seemingly no reason.
Hi-ya! I'm Kitty #153715. All you need to know about me is I hate cereal with a passion. Some people say I'm the Peter Griffin of the group. Can't wait to eat salad with you!

Howdy. My name is Kitty #731359. I make a mean spicy salami casserole. Do you think my best colour is neon pink or ivory? Who am I kidding, I look great in everything. Hey, you’re pretty and I’m cute. Together we’d be Pretty Cute.

I see you. My name is 💙 Lapis 💙 Summerbonnet, and before you ask, no, it's not short for anything. I ate ice cream with fish sauce on it and now my tummy hurts. In high school I was voted "most likely to impersonate Whitney Houston" and it definitely came true.

Hey! It's me, Skeletonne. I've spent years spooking Page's warriors for their trick-or-treat loot, and I've finally done the impossible: collected 1,000 kilograms of Salmon treats from those Burmilla bastards.
Oh heyyy. I am Sister Purrdaze. I shall call you Mr. Weatherbee. Me and Shia LaBeouf don't talk anymore. Pffft, whatever.

Hi-ya! I'm Eva Burnhard. I'm a Culinary Sanitation Specialist by day, and I like running a podcast by night. I'm convinced that that one day cats will rule this planet. One day I'll prove it. I hope we can be hairy friends.

Top o' the muffin to ya. My name is Lilac Spottencaten. I work as a Train Conductor, and I also moonlight as a Bumblebee impersonator. Some call me tantalizing, others call me outspoken, but really, the best description for me is brilliant. GET OUT OF MY ROOM!

What's up. I'm General Tickfuzzle, student of Balthazaar of the Unknown Lands. Did you know Breakfast at Tiffany's is really about this koala bear that gets covered in McChicken sauce? It's in the subtext. Don't even think about it.

Hey! Ho! Let's go! I'm Yoko Dooguts. I'm pretty sure I'm part labradoodle, I hope that doesn't bother you. At night, I like to put mint green paint all over my body and press up against buildings. I call it "making paint angels". I can't talk here, there are too many eavesdroppers around.
Oy! I'm Lala Gobhun! I enjoy long walks and coughing up furballs. I try to live my life the way I think Michael Scott would. Fly, you fool.

Hello. I'm 💙 Lapis  💙 Butterscotch. I'm dangerous and brilliant, and sometimes even fuzzy. I'm really into collecting sauerkraut right now. My mother might not approve of you, but that only makes me want to spend time with you even more.

Hey, what's up, hello. They call me Reindeer #317. Hey, got any horseradish on you? I'm always hungry. Believe it or not, tricking babies is seriously exhilarating. You should try it some time. Have you seen my thick-frame glasses?

Hello darkness, my old friend. My name is Loki Poopdonald. My best friend is a selkie. I'm convinced I'm the reincarnation of Marie Antoinette but I hit my kneecaps when I was a kitten so who knows. Why I oughta!

Have a seat, human, and let me tell you about the Cosmos, for I am Leopard x2, MM x2., father of intercatalactic travel. When we first journeyed the stars, we discovered an ancient ecosystem of Planets, Stars, and Celestial Cats. A spoon destroyed our ship and right when we were about to run out of sweets, friendly cats saved the day.
Good morning! I'm Founder Cat 28. In high school, I was voted school jock. I once pawed at a chimpanzee. I don't like to talk about it. Purrhaps this is the beginning of a beautiful relationship.

Ho there, warrior! I'm Bartholomeow. Amazing Traits.., master of deception and knitting. But really, I'm just a low-key Kitty who enjoys playing with their stringshot. Just don't give me mead, or else I'm known to spin quite a yarn.

*hissing noises*! Exclusive • Gen 0 •  Kit here. I'm here to enjoy fighting the patriarchy and tripping my owner. I'm convinced that that one day cats will rule this planet. One day I'll prove it. Can you make my brilliant dreams come true?
I see you. I'm 🧬 Gen 1 H1 Gene Swap, herald of the otherworld. I think I would have been voted "most likely to end up a street cat" if I had stayed in school. Did we just become best friends?

Sup! My name is 🥉 Uncommon Gen 1 Mewt. I work as a Firefighter, and I also moonlight as a Zoidberg impersonator. My squad always tells me to be more superficial, but meh. If you were a cheese, I'd say you'd be feta.
Top of the mornin' to ya. Oy. Hi friend. I'm Beatlesque: Salty Mewt, UNIQUE. I once slid into Kristen Wiig's DMs. I'm single and ready to mingle.
I'm Brave Flabguts, how the hell are ya!? I combine the best qualities of Diane Keaton, Napoleon Bonaparte, and The Backstreet Boys. Our auras seem aligned. I'm pawsitive this was meant to be.
Hi-ya. I am the one and only Red Dot. If I could be anybody in the world, it would be Hermione Granger. Also, I love McDonalds happy meals.

Greetings, kind purr! My name's Page and I'm a very good and clever kitten with a lot to offer the world! I have squired with the greatest of knights: there was Sir Face (they were a bit shallow), Sir Port (a very kind cat), and of course, Sir Prise (she was amazing). And now I have you! Gosh! I must be the luckiest kitten in the world!
Yo yo yo! My name is Nisse Biplater. Let's get to know each other better. I really want to paw a nice dolphin one day, is that weird? GET OUT OF MY ROOM!
Bark...errr, meow. I'm President Fluffyobie. I'm a cat, but I've always felt more like I belong in the panda family. Pffft, whatever.
*bows*, I'm Catnip Catwidgey, but what's in a name, anyway? I'm descended from Black Panther. I'd flex for you, but I don't want to ruin my snowshoes.
Hi-ya! I'm Gen 4 #3. I believe the world is flat. Sometimes I daydream of a life full of eating until I loathe myself, lasagna, and jump-roping. Let's pawty!

Hello! I'm called Briciola Demonbuncle. I like long walks on the beach and salsa. Pursuing a career in being a Chef has been exhausting, so I'm switching paths to be become a Balloon Captain. Let's connect on Neopets.

Ciao! My name is 💙 Lapis 💙 Ruhroh. I'm ambidextrous, you're lovable, let's connect. I like to collect knee-high socks. If you're nice enough, maybe I'll give you one. I love playing The Sims. Wanna join me?

Hey cutie! I'm G0. I want to live in a world where people believe that one day cats will rule this planet. It wasn't heavily publicized, but I once had a brief relationship with Hobbes. We're so fur-tunate to have found each other!
Bark...errr, meow. I'm Final Frontier & Kaleidoscope.. All I want in life is to listen to my Luke Bryan CDs in peace. Is that too much to ask? I heard Michael Cera has a crush on me. Meh.
Shalom! I'm RealityTV Junky | G15 barkbrow. In high school, I was voted school jock. When I'm not swiping left, I'm watching reality tv! I hope we can be preposterous friends.
En Taro Adun. I'm Marlin. I love to party with Lady Gaga, we get up to shenanigans together. I honestly would rather do anything else besides watch Caddyshack. Please pay attention to me.

Oh heyyy. My name is Purebred: Alicorn. BIS.. As a young kitten, I was always trying to swallow ribbons, but I think I've grown out of that. Every Tuesday evening I watch tv and binge on cereal. It makes the rest of the week bearable. If you can prove the reason we never find dead Bigfoots is because aliens take their bodies away then I'll eat my stockings right here, right now.
Howdy! My name is Timbers #314. I work as a Storm Chaser, and I also moonlight as a the Black Ranger impersonator. Whenever I eat flaming tacos my pee turns yellow. Is that normal? À Bientôt!
*tips hat*. I'm Lady Foofoo. Let's cut to the chase. If you'll just give me 30 seconds of your time, I can prove beyond a doubt that snake people run the world. Can I have your watch?
Ni hao! I'm Boots Fluffyzap, at least that's what they're calling me these days. I can whistle any Tom Jones song. It's a weird talent, but it entertains most people. Meowza.

Why hello there, I'm Shoshannah Proudtime. No, it's not pronounced Shoshannah Proudtime, it's pronounced Shoshannah Proudtime. I used to have a pet giant. Its name was Eva Peron. Can you explain where babies come from? Asking for a friend...

Top o' the muffin to ya! I'm 💙 Lapis 💙  padparadscha. I dare you to say my name three times in front of a mirror! I have made a mixtape for a duet with Snoop Dogg, but I'm having a hard time tracking them down. You can help, right? Good talk, catch ya later!
What gives. My name is Tzar Stoicbip. I pretty much only listen to Dropkick Murphys. I went to school with Lucifer, back then that was one saucy cat. I once berated a medusa, it was glorious.
Hai. Please call me Micio Queenhun or else I may scratch. When I was a kitten I was convinced I was actually a secret fairy. That turned out to be false. My celebrity crush is Ryan Gosling.
Mahalo! I'm 🐰. I'm a Dogwalker by day, and I like people-watching by night. I once got in a fight with a labradoodle, and won. Will you be the pickles to my maple syrup?
Listen up! I'm Katze Pharoahbaloo, feline warrior of a magical realm I can't tell you about. I used to love running a podcast, until the accident. Welp, seeya later.
*deadpan stare*! I'm 💀Sparrrrowww💀. I collect brooches and I love chorizo sausage. I love to eat whiskies while riding the bus. I look forward to stalking crows with you.

Top o' the muffin to ya! I'm Timbers: #357. I enjoy long saunters across your countertop and grooming myself on your pillow. I've never actually finished Jerry Maguire, I get too distracted with riding unicorns. Can you buy me some catnip? I'll get you back, I promise.
先生女士们！! 老喵我叫 3/4 Lion needs manx！如果你也讨厌三文鱼刺身的味道，我想我们一定可以成为好喵友！ 本喵对 所有名人都是外星人深信不疑，总一天我会证实给你看。 希望我俩可以成为最喵伙伴！

Greetings, acolyte, I am Purrspero. Purebred Virgin., master of the arcane arts and batting at string. I wield unfathomable power and still nap 16 hours a day. I offer my mystical abilities only to the worthiest lords and ladies of the KittyVerse, like you.

I'm here, I'm bad at rhymes, I'm Kitty Pride 2+-3-4! Be proud, be vivid, and be yourself. I could tone it down, but then I'd be lion to myself. Of course, not everyone can afford to be as colourful as I am, but I'm lucky — one of my ancestors was a non-binary landowner and there was gold in them/their hills.

Check it. I'm known as Fluffy Sillylater. I have a complicated past, but I'm ready for a new beginning. Believe it or not, prank-calling celebrities is seriously exhilarating. You should try it some time. Have you seen my stockings?
RAWR XD. I'm Minu Spicypookie, your new best fur-end. During my kitten days, I got lost in the fog with Patrick Star. Until our next encounter...

Dia dhuit, I'm Pure Clover: 4/4 Emeraldgreen.! Oof, I rode in here on a rainbow and those things aren't as soft as they look. Have you seen my pot o' gold? I swear I left it right here... Oh well, I don't need piles o' shinies to know I'm the luckiest cat in the KittyVerse––I get to hang out with you!

Allo, I'm Ari Meannoggin. No, it's not pronounced Ari Meannoggin, it's pronounced Ari Meannoggin. Let's spend the whole day listening to Metallica together. I want to know what love is. I want you to show me.

Well look who it is! I'm Brave Hypersmoosh. Roses are Pantone 18-3838 ultra violet, violets are orangesoda, I'm weird. I'm trying to consume at least one serving of boiled eggs every day. It's a newer health thing I read about on the web. Can I have your watch?

Namaste. I'm chart hinto pure ganado. My friends describe me as seductive and lovely. Sometimes I daydream of a life full of biting ankles, prank-calling celebrities, and cantaloupe. We can be friends, but keep the ultra purrsonal stuff to yourself, please.

Hey! Ho! Let's go. I'm Guile Bipmami. And you are? Would you believe me if I told you milk was invented by the government as a way to subdue the cat population? What if I said free will does not exist? Let's watch Rick and Morty together.

Yaya. I'm Shamanbutt McPawtucker Ze2nd, collector of marbles and breaker of hearts. I spend all my money on Paula Abdul records and I don't even have a record player yet. Can you explain where babies come from? Asking for a friend...
Yikes! You scared me. The name's Dieter Pharoahness. I'd say the hip panda is my spirit animal. I see those eyes you're giving me. *wink*

Have a seat, human, and let me tell you about the Cosmos, for I am Cosmocat with 4 double trraits, father of intercatalactic travel. When we first journeyed the stars, we discovered an ancient ecosystem of Planets, Stars, and Celestial Cats. A spoon destroyed our ship and right when we were about to run out of sweets, friendly cats saved the day.
Ooops lol, please refer to me as Kaka Zippywampus, and only that. My band's sound is a mix of The Strokes and Skrillex. À Bientôt!
Good day! SamGam / G23 barkbrown here. I'm here to enjoy riding unicorns and taking selfies. Some people say I'm the Samwise Gamgee of the group. It's pawesome to meet you!

Welcome! My name is 859127, but I prefer to be addressed as "your highness". My best dress-up costume ever was when I impersonated Marissa Cooper. I'm a kitty, you're a human, this friendship is our destiny.

En Taro Adun. I'm Kiisu Woonano. Roses are mauveover, violets are aquamarine, I'm weird. I was going to become a Waste Management Technician, but then I found out the moon landing was produced by Steven Spielberg. Ta-ta for now.

Sup playa! I'm Kitty #618333. I'm a professional Dogwalker and I love ice cream. It wasn't heavily publicized, but I once had a brief relationship with Salem . I look forward to picking flowers with you.

*yawn* Sorry, you caught me napping. I seem to have lost my name tag, but I'm Sir Yodelki. I once entered a litter-eating contest just because it's better to burn out than to fade away. I did not win. I heard Jeff Goldblum has a crush on me. Meh.
What gives. I am Farfalle Waddleflip, come closer, child. Pursuing a career in being a Aerobics Athlete has been exhausting, so I'm switching paths to be become a Dogwalker. Shhhh, don't speak.
Listen up. My name is Hyacinth JuJu Unicorn.. I love to wear sky blue. I really want to become a Pest Exterminator. I dream about it every day. Can you handle me?

Sup playa, my name is Ari Sunnynano, but you may address me as supreme cat overlord. I combine the strength of the patagonian mara with the grace of the raven. My New Year's resolution is to be more noxious.
Hello! I'm Kitty #533401. I work as a Ringmaster and I love staying woke. If you enjoy watching Aristocats, we'll get along just fine. Pleased to make your acquiantance.
*waves*. I'm ♥♥Kit Meowcaw♥♥. Are you the one who passed out in front of me earlier? I'm totally obsessed with Felix the Cat. Can you handle me?
Ugh! I'm Ari Allmust. Pleased to meet you. My favourite way to vacation is watching Netflix and only consuming wet food. Let's go eating fine cheeses together!
Heyo! I'm Foofoo Kinkygoo, your new best fur-end. I listened to Cher before it was cool. Fancy Cats are cool, but I'm more interested in breeding for love.

Hello. My name is Young Bobobum. I'm garish, you're atomic, let's connect. I honestly would rather do anything else besides watch Transformers. Sometimes, when I'm circumnavigating the globe, I stop and think, isn't it crazy that the world is flat.
Oh hi! I'm Mauve Goose / G16 Mauveover. In high school, I was voted most likely to work at NASA. My secret indulgence is cantaloupe. Let's get busy!

Hiya. My name is Ari Lildub, but I'm in the process of legally changing it to Elijah Wood. Some call me belligerent, others call me headstrong, but really, the best description for me is bubbly. I eat in my sleep, I hope that's not going to be a problem.

What's up! Rocket here. I'm here to enjoy tricking babies and watching Stranger Things. I am 44% elf, 69% Dispensary Clerk, and otherwise bad at math. We can be friends, but keep the ultra purrsonal stuff to yourself, please.
RAWR XD. I'm Minu Spicypookie, your new best fur-end. During my kitten days, I got lost in the fog with Patrick Star. Until our next encounter...
Good day! I'm DUCAT SPECTACULAR!!!. In high school, I was voted biggest teacher's pet. I once made a goose trot. Our friendship will be wondrous, fabulous, and full of salad.

Why hello there! I'm Orangesoda X Coffee Combo! I enjoy long walks and coughing up furballs. This one time, at band camp, I was voted "most likely to run for president". I once bit a troll, it was glorious.
Hi friend. You may call me SHAMROCK X2. I honestly would rather do anything else besides watch Avengers: Infinity War. Word on the street is House of the Dead is the best game of all time. All time!
Heyo! I'm Cereal Killer / G21. I'm a professional Dispensary Clerk and I love cereal. My secret indulgence is salad. I like your face.
Where are my manners. The name's Yoyo Hissnic. I'm a cat, but I've always felt more like I belong in the rhino family. Let's go to my litter box, it's where I conduct all my meetings.
Hark! I'm Taters Twinklepet. My squad always tells me to be more exuberant, but meh. Ever since I met Jonah Hill I've believed sometimes when we touch, the honesty's too much.
Yo. My name is Misty Ughsmookie, and before you ask, no, it's not short for anything. I keep some blue cheese under my pillow in case of emergencies. Don't @ me.
What's up! I'm Kitty #354237. In high school, I was voted biggest teacher's pet. I once got in a fight with a rabbit, and won. Can you make my wondrous dreams come true?
Uh, hi! I'm Kitty #320319. I enjoy riding dirty, tripping my owner, and being a nevernude. I once got in a fight with a dog, and won. Let's pawty!
*hissing noises*! I'm Bashfull Tiger / G22 barkbrown. I believe the world is flat. It wasn't heavily publicized, but I once had a brief relationship with Hobbes. Can't wait to eat salad with you!
Hai, my name is Midnight Sullentooth, but I'll also respond to Lady Gaga. Unlike most cats, I always land on my tummy. Would you believe that Shia LaBeouf is just like you and me?

*winces*. My name is Royal Purple Rorschach.. Let's cut to the chase: I like playing Bonbon Smash. Wanna join? I try to live my life the way I think Wallace Wells would. I don't have time for new friends, but I'll make an exception for you.
